# <span style="font-family: 'VT323', monospace;">ENA Clock</span>
![](img/meta/readme/ena-clock-banner-windowstheme.png)

<span style="font-family: 'VT323', monospace;">Meet the (un)official ENA watchface for Bangle.js 2, inspired by Joel Guerra's popular [ENA series!](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xUwJWv38FpY&list=PLhPaJURyApsoMQDaoft5t0l0iAwUOLtlM&index=2)</span>

<span style="font-family: 'VT323', monospace;">In anticipation for the release of *ENA: Dream BBQ*, I've decided to make a watchface that honors ENA's first season.</span>


## <span style="font-family: 'VT323', monospace;">Enjoy these sceneic views of the ENAverse!</span>

<span style="font-family: 'VT323', monospace;">Hourglass Meadow (Beach)</span>

![](img/meta/readme/watchfaces/hmb.png)

## <span style="font-family: 'VT323', monospace;">Planned watchfaces & content</span>
- Watchface: Hourglass Meadow (Hills)
- Watchface: Mannequin Expanse
- Watchface: Overworld
- Watchface: Maze
- Watchface: Desert
- Watchface: Stairway Void
- Watchface: Hourglass Meadow (Garden)
- Content: Animated characters, including (but not limited to) ENA and Moony
- Content: Lots of stuff from Season 2!



## <span style="font-family: 'VT323', monospace;">Usage</span>

Install, and select as your default watch face. That's it!

## <span style="font-family: 'VT323', monospace;">Features</span>

- Telling time in a very fashonable manor

## <span style="font-family: 'VT323', monospace;">Requests</span>

Feel free to contact me with any questions or ideas regarding this watchface! Contact links are provided on my [GitHub Page](https://github.com/BraidenPsiuk).
